# Scripts

## What is contained within this directory?

This directory contains the javascript scripts, which allow the webpage to be more interactive and functional.

## Files contained within this directory:

### Animate
This file stores animations which are applied to elements on the webpage.

### Categories
This file contains functions which relate to the category selection portion of the main page, including how the Flipper element is ordered.

### Data
This file contains extra functions which control the filtering and manipulation of data for fetching categories.

### Filter
This file handles the filtering of prompt components, returning the filtered elements to the page.

### Homedragger
This file stores the functions which control the 'drag'n'drop' elements of the page, as we as the copy and edit button functionalities.